(1 - Install) Tj
0 -13 Td
(1. Go to the official Hermes site: https://hermes-agent.nousresearch.com/) Tj
0 -13 Td
(2. Download Hermes for your computer \(Mac or Windows\) and follow their install steps.) Tj
0 -13 Td
(3. Open it. When setup asks about an AI model/provider, read section 1.7 below first - there) Tj
0 -13 Td
(  are free and low-cost routes.) Tj
0 -13 Td
() Tj
0 -13 Td
(1.5 - Permissions - give it a room, not the house) Tj
0 -13 Td
(At some point Hermes will ask for permission to access files. This is the moment that) Tj
0 -13 Td
(  matters most:) Tj
0 -13 Td
() Tj
0 -13 Td
(- Grant access ONLY to your My-Nurse-AI-OS folder - the one from the Starter Kit. Nothing) Tj
0 -13 Td
(  else.) Tj
0 -13 Td
(- Decline anything broader - full disk, Desktop, Downloads, Photos. If you accidentally) Tj
0 -13 Td
(  grant more, you can remove it later in your computer's privacy settings.) Tj
0 -13 Td
(- Think of it like a float nurse's badge: access to the assigned unit, not every floor of) Tj
0 -13 Td
(  the hospital. Hermes does excellent work in its unit. It has no business wandering the) Tj
0 -13 Td
(  building.) Tj
0 -13 Td
() Tj
0 -13 Td
(1.7 - Choose how your AI is powered - free and low-cost routes) Tj
0 -13 Td
(Hermes itself is free and open-source. Any cost comes from the AI model that powers it -) Tj
0 -13 Td
(  think of Hermes as the IV pump, free, and the model as what runs through it, metered by) Tj
0 -13 Td
(  use. Two routes:) Tj
0 -13 Td
() Tj
0 -13 Td
(Route A - the Nous subscription. The simplest: one subscription, everything handled. Choose) Tj
0 -13 Td
(  it during setup and skip the rest of this step.) Tj
0 -13 Td
() Tj
0 -13 Td
(Route B - Bring Your Own Keys \(most cost-effective - can be nearly free\). In Hermes setup,) Tj
0 -13 Td
(  choose Full Setup \(not the default subscription option\), then Bring Your Own Keys. We) Tj
0 -13 Td
(  recommend OpenRouter \(https://openrouter.ai\) - one free account, one API key, and a whole) Tj
0 -13 Td
(  menu of models, including free and very low-cost ones. Then:) Tj
0 -13 Td
() Tj
0 -13 Td
(1. Create an account at openrouter.ai and generate an API key from your dashboard.) Tj
0 -13 Td
(2. Set a spending limit in OpenRouter first - your safety rail against surprise bills. Start) Tj
0 -13 Td
(  at a few dollars; you can always raise it.) Tj
0 -13 Td
(3. In Hermes setup, choose OpenRouter as your provider and paste your key.) Tj
0 -13 Td
(4. Pick a model - start with a free or low-cost one. Ask Hermes for something simple to) Tj
0 -13 Td
