0 -13 Td
() Tj
0 -13 Td
(Why these two files matter more than everything else: a powerful AI is like a powerful horse) Tj
0 -13 Td
(  - magnificent, and dangerous without a harness. The Starter Kit and your SOUL file are the) Tj
0 -13 Td
(  harness. The SOUL file gives the engine your values, your boundaries, the lines it may) Tj
0 -13 Td
