(Post-procedure care - working the system until it's muscle memory) Tj
0 -13 Td
(You don't memorize features. You see the routine once in your mind, and your hands follow.) Tj
0 -13 Td
(  Seven habits:) Tj
0 -13 Td
() Tj
0 -13 Td
(1 - Triage the task, then pick the model. Simple work - quick questions, summaries,) Tj
0 -13 Td
(  rewrites, brainstorming - gets a free or cheap model. Heavy work - multi-step planning,) Tj
0 -13 Td
(  long documents, coding, deep troubleshooting - gets a stronger reasoning model. Need it to) Tj
0 -13 Td
(  look at a screenshot or diagram? Pick a vision-capable one. You don't call the code team) Tj
0 -13 Td
(  for a splinter: start cheap, escalate when the task needs it.) Tj
0 -13 Td
() Tj
0 -13 Td
(2 - One session per topic - one chart per patient. Don't mix the budget, the side gig, and) Tj
0 -13 Td
(  the CCRN plan in one conversation - details blend and answers get muddy. New topic, new) Tj
0 -13 Td
(  session.) Tj
0 -13 Td
() Tj
0 -13 Td
(3 - Projects are care plans; sessions are shifts. A session is one conversation. For) Tj
0 -13 Td
(  anything ongoing - a course you're building, a business plan, a family project - use a) Tj
0 -13 Td
(  Project: a workspace where files, goals, and conversations stay together, so you never) Tj
0 -13 Td
(  start from scratch.) Tj
0 -13 Td
() Tj
0 -13 Td
(4 - Call a consult - use personas. Tell Hermes who to be, and the depth and style of the) Tj
0 -13 Td
(  answer change with it: "Act as a plain-language tutor and explain this error step by) Tj
0 -13 Td
(  step." - "Act as a startup strategist and review my plan for risks and next moves.") Tj
0 -13 Td
() Tj
0 -13 Td
(5 - When unsure, ask the assistant itself. You never need the perfect prompt: "What's the) Tj
0 -13 Td
(  best next step?" - "Ask me the questions you need before we continue." - "Break this into) Tj
0 -13 Td
(  simple steps." - "Which model should I use for this task?") Tj
0 -13 Td
() Tj
0 -13 Td
(6 - Troubleshoot with screenshots - show, don't describe. Hand over the telemetry strip) Tj
0 -13 Td
(  instead of describing it. Share the screenshot plus: what you were trying to do, what) Tj
0 -13 Td
(  happened instead, the exact error, and what you've already tried. Never include API keys) Tj
0 -13 Td
(  or passwords in a screenshot - crop or blur them first.) Tj
0 -13 Td
() Tj
0 -13 Td
(7 - Steward the spend. Watch usage the way you watch supplies: spending limits on, drafts on) Tj
0 -13 Td
(  cheap models, strong models saved for final reasoning, no huge files unless the task truly) Tj
0 -13 Td
(  needs them.) Tj
0 -13 Td
() Tj
0 -13 Td
(The everyday routine - say it until your hands know it: right model for the task - new) Tj
0 -13 Td
(  session for a new topic - a project for ongoing work - a persona for specialist output -) Tj
0 -13 Td
(  ask when unsure - show a screenshot when stuck - escalate the model only when needed.) Tj
0 -13 Td
() Tj
0 -13 Td
(Five phrases that do most of the work) Tj
0 -13 Td
(You say  |  Hermes does) Tj
0 -13 Td
("Run my morning huddle."  |  Asks your #1 priority, offers three ways to help) Tj
0 -13 Td
("Give me a Kardex entry for this session."  |  Writes a 5-line handoff note to save in) Tj
0 -13 Td
(  03-Memory) Tj
0 -13 Td
("Make that correction permanent."  |  Turns your feedback into a standing rule) Tj
0 -13 Td
("Before you start, interview me like an admission assessment."  |  Asks questions before big) Tj
0 -13 Td
(  tasks instead of guessing) Tj
0 -13 Td
("Show me your plan before you do anything."  |  Keeps your hand on every decision) Tj
0 -13 Td
() Tj
